Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:32.71,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,UPACARA PENERIMAAN MURID BARU\NHORE! HARI PERTAMA!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.52,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,OSIS
