Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini siapa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungil, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masami, kau seorang pelatih, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau bantu aku\Nmelihat postur larinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku bahkan belum lulus...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lulus tidaklah penting! Pada saatnya\Nkau akan menjadi pelatih, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah memberimu diskon sewa,\Njadi bantulah aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak kecil ini\Ntinggal di apartemenku yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya suatu hari nanti\Ndia mau pergi ke Tracen yang indah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhku tak seperti dulu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana? Maukah kau menuruti\Npermintaan terakhir orang tua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa namamu, Anak Kecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamamo Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan memanggilmu Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Komiyama Masami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu denganmu, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu kau juga, Komi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Komi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya sudah beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jadi, keputusanmu sudah mantap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, keputusanku sudah bulat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Rudolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini? Kau tak perlu minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini yang kau mau, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan kubiarkan\Nsiapa pun berbicara menentangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan sisanya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berutang padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kapan-kapan\Naku bisa mentraktirmu takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamamo Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga tak ada penyesalan di lombamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pastinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong tunggu di sini\Nsampai kami memanggilmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, merepotkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci konferensi pers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo segera selesaikan ini\Nagar aku bisa kembali berlatih...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, tak mungkin! Apelnya enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Oguri, kau harus mencoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kau habiskan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kabar ayahmu baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih suka mengendap-endap\Nmendekati orang, Musaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa bilang aku mengendap-endap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang tak melihatku\Nuntuk beberapa alasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu seharusnya menjadi lelucon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang lidahmu tajam, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu kau selalu lari saat melihatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sudah lama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis Kecil Penyihir sudah tumbuh besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar sekarang\Nmereka bahkan memanggilmu Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu kehormatan untuk melawan\Ngenius muda yang terkenal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa berkata hal yang sama padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Satu-satunya pria yang selalu berdiri\Ndi antara ayahku dan kejayaan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pelatih legendaris dengan keahlian\Nyang membingungkan, hampir seperti sihir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah Peri
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ginjiro Musaka.\N- Jangan memanggilku itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu benci julukan bodoh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir itu cukup keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Oguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah menemukan apa yang kau cari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang aku cari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melihatnya\Ndari dekat dan personal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Belum... Aku masih mencari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kabar, Geng?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah! Ayo kita mulai\Nkonferensi pers ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, seseorang\Nbersemangat sekali hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti Creek!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau bintang\Nyang mencuri perhatian di Kikuka Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga! Apa mungkin kau menontonnya?\NAku hargai dukungannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai ucapan terima kasih,\Naku suapi apel. Buka mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah. Tidak perlu berterima kasih\Nkarena aku menonton balapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, kau harus coba.\NRasanya sangat mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Sekarang aku tak lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Tamamo Cross sangat tak suka apel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak... Ya... Begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus ambil beberapa\Nuntuk Chiyo dan yang lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan asumsi satu apel 300 gram\Ndan dua di antaranya sudah dimakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}asupan kalori hari ini adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, Pelatih...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bergumam hal-hal acak lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelatih?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf aku tak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pelatih Dicta Striker, Kouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia besar, 'kan? Tingginya dua meter pas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku belum pernah\Nmelihatmu di sekolah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cenderung diam di gedung klub kami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ada waktu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada masalah, Tama?\NBukankah mereka segera memanggil kita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lomba kita selanjutnya Arima Kinen, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini pertama kalinya kau di Nakayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akan seru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Ogurin. Aku tak yakin apa kau tahu,\Ntapi Arima Kinen itu lomba penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Maksudku, sangat penting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini pertarungan habis-habisan\Nantara para pembalap terbaik tahun ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pertarungan terakhir untuk melihat\Nsiapa yang berdiri di puncak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rekor balapanmu dan generasimu\Ntak penting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau menang, kau akan selamanya dikenal\Nsebagai pembalap terbaik di Jepang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa pasti itu alasannya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}banyak pelari mengakhiri kariernya\Ndengan lomba ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akui, mereka mungkin tahu sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, mengakhiri karier\Ndengan kesuksesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oguri Cap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arima Kinen akan menjadi\Nbalapan terakhirku di Twinkle Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terakhir untukmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu... Kau bercanda, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan ini.\NSeluruh Jepang menonton Arima Kinen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau memenangkan lomba terbesar\Nmelawan pembalap terbaik di negara ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}itu membuktikan\Naku yang terbaik di Jepang,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu aku bisa meninggalkan\Ndunia balapan dalam kesuksesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akhir yang bahagia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhir bahagia untuk siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa mengalahkanmu\Nkalau kau tak ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau yang menganggapku\Nsebagai rivalmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kita berdua...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada sesuatu\Nyang membuatmu berhenti, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin kau siap untuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tutup mulutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang mau berhenti, maka aku berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat mau mengalahkanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kau punya satu kesempatan terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalahkan aku di Arima Kinen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sebelum aku sadar,\Nkonferensi pers itu sudah dimulai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Creek dan Dicta bicara tentang\Nmotivasi untuk balapan mendatang,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}lalu Tama mengumumkan ini menjadi\Nbalapan terakhirnya di Twinkle Series.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pers... Tidak, seluruh Jepang terkejut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kukira Tamamo Cross akan selalu\Nmenjadi rivalku. Tapi kurasa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}aku salah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku bahkan tak ingat bilang apa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus hari ini, Pelatih Komiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kau, Belno... Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tadi ramai sekali, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa selalu seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mereka agak menyebalkan hari ini,\Nmengingat pengumuman kami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengejutkan sekali. Sulit dipercaya\NArima Kinen akan menjadi yang terakhir...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kebetulan dia sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sepertinya dia tak membenci apel,\Ntapi tetap menolak memakannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sejujurnya, sikapnya yang ceria\Nterasa agak dipaksakan hari ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penilaianmu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak alasan di balik keputusannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi makannya memang sedikit.\NSelain itu, dia agak sensitif.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku selalu tahu\Nhari ini akan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia tak dapat nutrisi yang cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Dia sangat sehat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku membuat makanannya ekstra bergizi\Nuntuk mengimbangi kebiasaan makannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, kau membuatkan makanannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tugasku sebagai pelatih, memikirkan\Napa yang paling cocok dengan kebutuhannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mungkin\Nbukan pelatih terbaik di Jepang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tak seorang pun di dunia ini\Nyang lebih mengenal Tama dibanding aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku penasaran... Apa saran-saranku\Nsudah sesuai untuk Oguri?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa yang paling cocok untuk kebutuhannya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Pelatih Komiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang harus aku kerjakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga aku tak membantu musuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak bagus...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Kalau aku tak segera menemukan jawabannya,\Nakan terlambat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo bersenang-senang, Oguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan berlari 2.500 meter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kita akan mulai di sini\Nsupaya ada bukit di tanda 200 meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Arima...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau menyadarinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap saja ini gladi bersih\Nuntuk lomba yang sebenarnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ringan dan santai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ringan dan santai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini terasa seperti balapan asli!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Zona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat menginginkannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kalau begini, kau tak akan pernah tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Oguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kau memenangkan tiga\Ndari empat balapan sejak debutmu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu termasuk kemenangan\Ndi G1 Hanshin Junior Stakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dicta Striker, sebagai jagoan saat ini\Ndi generasimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maukah kau berbagi rencanamu untuk Klasik?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:14:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari segi jarak,\Naku tak tahu tentang Kikuka Sho,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku pasti mengikuti\NSatsuki Sho dan Derby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satsuki Sho dan Derby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada pemikiran yang mau\Nkau bagikan pada para fanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemikiran, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Klasik atau bukan,\Naku tak pernah berencana untuk kalah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu tak ada yang sempurna,\Ntapi kukira seharusnya dia genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia terlalu dini\Nmencapai puncak, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, dia tak dapat\Nsatu pun kemenangan di musim semi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak sesuai ekspektasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dicta Striker sudah tamat, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Apa masalah mereka!\NBerhenti memperlakukanku seperti sampah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Akan kutunjukkan pada kalian...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalian semua!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pembalap memasuki tikungan!\NTikungan ketiga di depan mata!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meikun Okan memimpin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Lebih unggul satu langkah,\Ndia mencapai tanda 600 meter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dicta Striker...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Memang, itu G3 di daerah terpencil,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia bodoh karena melawan\Ndua juara Derby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini dia benar-benar putus asa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau dia kalah di sini,\Nmaka kita tahu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Max... Bukan, itu Dicta Striker!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dicta Striker!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dicta Striker melesat dari luar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia perjuangkan posisi ketiga\Nsaat kami berbicara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jangan kalian berani...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jangan berani bilang aku sudah tamat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Akan kutunjukkan pada kalian semua!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku akan pertaruhkan semuanya\Nuntuk melakukannya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seolah aku sudah terlahir kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seolah seluruh tubuhku\Nmendidih dengan energi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata-kata tak bisa menggambarkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak saat itu, aku tak bisa\Nmelawan dorongan yang makin besar ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau berdiri di puncak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kulawan pembalap yang makin kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku akan mengalahkan\Nmasing-masing dari mereka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan membuktikan bahwa aku yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Dari 2.500 meter di Arena Balap Nakayama,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}rintangan terbesar\Ntentu saja tanjakan yang curam itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tanjakan membutuhkan teknik.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak bisa melakukannya\Nhanya dengan kekuatan seperti hal lainnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku butuh strategi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku yakin bisa menemukan banyak jawaban\Nkalau melakukan riset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak seorang pun di dunia ini\Nyang lebih mengenal Tama dibanding aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Oguri mengambil posisi\Ncondong ke depan saat berlari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia tak seperti pembalap lainnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Melakukan lomba ini sesuai aturan\Nbukanlah jawabannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi pasti ada solusi lain\Nyang berhasil untuk Oguri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Setelah melihat Tamamo Cross\Ndi Tenno Sho musim gugur, aku tahu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia sudah berhasil menerobos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Lalu, kau hampir mencapainya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat bergabunglah dengan kami, Oguri Cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teroboslah dan buat aku\Nberjuang untuk kemenangan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu dia. Hampir sampai, Oguri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini alasannya kau adalah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kedatangan murid pindahan baru\Ndari Kasamatsu! Ini Oguri Cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kalian semua\Nakan memberikan sambutan hangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kasamatsu? Di mana itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Awalnya, aku hanya mengira\Nkau murid pindahan yang unik.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Tidak kurang, tak lebih.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi sebelum aku menyadarinya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Oguri Cap melesat,\Nmeninggalkan mereka semua!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Oguri Cap tak terhentikan! Dia unggul\Nmencengangkan selisih tujuh langkah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meninggalkan semua orang,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dia melewati garis finis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Juara pertama adalah Oguri Cap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bintang Kasamatsu bersinar,\Nbahkan menyilaukan pembalap nasional!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pembalap ini mungkin saja\Njagoan sejati di generasinya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dicta Striker, sebagai jagoan saat ini\Ndi generasimu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}maukah kau berbagi rencanamu untuk Klasik?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pantas saja orang bilang\Ndia bisa menjadi juara Derby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kau tahu, Oguri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mungkin bagimu, aku teman sekelas biasa,\Nyang bahkan belum pernah balapan denganmu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi bagiku, kau adalah{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}rivalku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku bisa melakukannya,\Ntak mungkin kau tak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Oguri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan! Siapa yang mau kau ungguli?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Siapa yang mau aku ungguli...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa kau berlari?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang mendorongmu untuk balapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mau pergi lebih jauh dari siapa pun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mau berlari\Nlebih cepat dari siapa pun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mau lebih kuat dari siapa pun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Benar... Aku mau mengungguli{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}semua rivalku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rivalku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bukan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Siapa yang mau aku ungguli?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak ada orang lain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kembali dan makan sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu tadi? Kau takut kalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak melewati garis finis,\Njadi tak ada yang menang atau kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan melukai diri sendiri\Ndengan habis-habisan sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau yang bilang mau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bung.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kupikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melihat itu semua, Pelatih?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti biasanya, kau terlalu baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu alasanku melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak mau orang berkata\Nkemenanganku tak dihitung{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena dia tak dalam kondisi terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini yang disebut anak-anak {\i1}tsundere?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Mau ditendang?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawabannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Akhirnya, hari yang ditunggu-tunggu\Npara penggemar balap sudah tiba!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Saat angin musim dingin merusak kota,\Nhanya arena balap ini yang selamat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tentunya, tribun di sini hari ini\Nsangat panas, karena demam balap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Benar, Arena Balap Nakayama\Nhari ini benar-benar penuh sesak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sementara dunia merayakan Natal,\Npara fan menantikan pertarungan abad ini!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mengintip dari balik awan,\Nmatahari menyinari lintasan dan pembalap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Balapan hari ini, G1 Arima Kinen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}akan dimulai!{\i0}
